enchantment.alexsmobs.lavawax.desc: Nadaje Odporność na ogień jadącemu na desce okracznej.
enchantment.alexsmobs.serpentfriend.desc: Sprawia że Kościane Węże są neutralne dla jadącego na desce okracznej.
enchantment.alexsmobs.board_return.desc: Deska okraczna powraca do inwentarza gdy się zniszczy.
advancements.alexsmobs.root.title: Alex's Mobs
advancements.alexsmobs.crimson_mosquito_: Stwórz Larwę Karmazynowego Komara z Larwy i Specjalnej Kłujki
advancements.alexsmobs.blood_sprayer.des: Wytwórz Spryskiwacz Krwi z Łupów Karmazynowego Kamara
Oswój Spaczoną Żabę, Idealną Ochronę Przed każdym Owadem.
advancements.alexsmobs.hummingbird_feede: Craft a Hummingbird Feeder in order to keep hummingbirds nearby
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_grizzly_bear: Tame a Grizzly Bear by feeding it honey and salmon
advancements.alexsmobs.rattlesnake.title: No Step on Snake
advancements.alexsmobs.maraca.title: Mariachi?
advancements.alexsmobs.maraca.desc: Craft a Maraca with a Rattlesnake rattle
advancements.alexsmobs.la_cucaracha.desc: Give a Maraca to a cockroach and enjoy the show. ¡La Cucaracha!
advancements.alexsmobs.banana.title: Gone Bananas!
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_capuchin_mon: Tame a capuchin monkey with bananas
Receive a blessing from the great and noble sunbird
advancements.alexsmobs.sopa_de_macaco.de: Craft sopa de macaco with a banana peel
advancements.alexsmobs.crocodile.title: Chompy
advancements.alexsmobs.crocodile_chestpl: Craft a crocodile chestplate from many crocodile scutes
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_mantis_shrim: Tame a Mantis Shrimp with many feedings of Tropical Fish
advancements.alexsmobs.breed_crocodile.d: Breed two crocodiles with rotten flesh. Careful not to trample their eggs!
advancements.alexsmobs.spiked_scute.desc: Shear a moss-covered Alligator Snapping Turtle and obtain a Spiked Scute
advancements.alexsmobs.mantis_shrimp_buc: Sneak and give a tamed Mantis Shrimp a bucket of water so that it can live on land indefinitely
advancements.alexsmobs.orcas_might.title: Free Willy
advancements.alexsmobs.orcas_might.desc: Be granted a blessing from a wild Orca
advancements.alexsmobs.acacia_blossom.de: Obtain an Acacia Blossom from breaking Acacia Leaves
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant.des: Tame an elephant by feeding it Acacia Blossoms
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_elephant_tus: Tame a tusked elephant when it is a baby
advancements.alexsmobs.elephant_swag.des: Place a colored carpet on an elephant
advancements.alexsmobs.soul_vulture.desc: Encounter a Soul Vulture in the nether
advancements.alexsmobs.soul_heart.title: The Soul-ly Ghost
advancements.alexsmobs.soul_heart.desc: Obtain a soul heart from slaying a bloated Soul Vulture
advancements.alexsmobs.spectre.title: The Iron Curtain
advancements.alexsmobs.spectre.desc: Lure a Spectre in the end with a Soul Heart. Use a lead on them to hitch a ride!
advancements.alexsmobs.guster.title: Eye of The Storm
advancements.alexsmobs.guster.desc: Encounter a Guster during a stormy day in the desert
advancements.alexsmobs.gustmaker.title: I Am Become Guster
advancements.alexsmobs.gustmaker.desc: Craft a Gustmaker. Now you can make your own mini-storms!
advancements.alexsmobs.pocket_sand.title: Pocket Sand!
advancements.alexsmobs.pocket_sand.desc: Craft a Pocket Of Sand. Sha-sha!
advancements.alexsmobs.crimson_mosquito_: Feed a Crimson Mosquito a strange, fungal creature covered in Warped Fungus. Watch as the Crimson Mosquito transforms!
advancements.alexsmobs.warped_mosco_kill: Slay the Warped Mosco, the swole defender of the Warped Forest.
advancements.alexsmobs.hemolymph_blaster: Craft a Hemolyph Blaster, the ultimate upgrade to the Blood Sprayer.
advancements.alexsmobs.straddler.title: Straddle My Ol' Saddle
advancements.alexsmobs.straddler.desc: Encounter a Straddler in the Basalt Deltas.
advancements.alexsmobs.stradpole_feed.de: Feed a Stradpole some Mosquito Larva, in hopes of turning it into a Straddler.
advancements.alexsmobs.straddleboard.des: Craft a Straddleboard from some Netherite and Straddlerite.
advancements.alexsmobs.emu.title: It's an Emu!!!
advancements.alexsmobs.emu_dodge.title: Begun, The Emu War Has
advancements.alexsmobs.emu_dodge.desc: See an emu dodge a launched projectile.
advancements.alexsmobs.kangaroo.title: We do a little trolling...
advancements.alexsmobs.save_cachalot_wha: Save a beached Cachalot Whale by pushing it into the water, and then have it reward you by coughing up some Ambergris
advancements.alexsmobs.echolocator.title: Echo-muh-cation!
advancements.alexsmobs.echolocator.desc: Craft an Echolocator, which can reveal nearby caves
advancements.alexsmobs.endolocator.title: No End In Signt
advancements.alexsmobs.endolocator.desc: Craft an Endolocator, which can reveal nearby End Portal Frames
advancements.alexsmobs.stomp_leafcutter_: Stomp on a Leafcutter Anthill - beware the angry denizens within!
advancements.alexsmobs.gongylidia.title: Like a Truffle, with more Ant
advancements.alexsmobs.gongylidia.desc: Harvest Gongylidia from a Leafcutter Ant Chamber underground. Place Shroomlight near the chamber to make sure you don't upset the locals
advancements.alexsmobs.leafcutter_ant_pu: Obtain a Leafcutter Ant Pupa, which can be placed on dirt to start a Leafcutter Ant colony.
advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage.desc: Encounter an Enderiophage, a giant biomechanical construct found in the End Midlands. Be careful not to catch Ender Flu!
advancements.alexsmobs.capsid.title: Capsid-19
advancements.alexsmobs.capsid.desc: Obtain a Capsid from a slain Enderiophage. Use it to display items or to transfer them upwards
advancements.alexsmobs.ender_flu.title: Race Against The Clock
advancements.alexsmobs.ender_flu.desc: Catch the Ender Flu effect. Cure it by eating many Chorus Fruit or drinking milk. Be sure not to let it run its toll!
advancements.alexsmobs.enderiophage_rock: Craft an Enderiophage Rocket, which can be used in place of Firework Rockets when in the End.
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_bald_eagle.d: Tame a bald eagle with fish oil.
advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_glove.de: Craft a Falconry Glove from Leather and Hair of Bear. Use it to pick up and launch tamed eagles!
advancements.alexsmobs.falconry_hood.des: Craft a Falconry Hood from Leather and a Roadrunner Feather. Eagles wearing one can be manually directed!
advancements.alexsmobs.bald_eagle_challe: Kill any creature from 100 blocks away with an eagle wearing a hood.
advancements.alexsmobs.tigers_blessing.d: Receive a Tiger's Blessing after feeding it Porkchops, Chicken or other meats.
advancements.alexsmobs.tarantula_hawk.de: Encounter a Tarantula Hawk in a desert.
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_tarantula_ha: Tame a Tarantula Hawk by feeding it Spider Eyes.
advancements.alexsmobs.mysterious_worm.d: Create a Mysterious Worm by putting a Crimson Mosquito Larva in a Capsid.
Toss the Mysterious Worm into the void of the End, and prepare to meet the Void Worm.
advancements.alexsmobs.void_worm_split.d: Split a void worm in half by attacking one of its body segments. More worms, more problems!
advancements.alexsmobs.dimensional_carve: Using the drops of the Void Worm, create the Dimensional Carver, which allows you to dig through the fabric of reality to return home at any given point.
advancements.alexsmobs.seagull_steal.des: Have food stolen from your inventory by a seagull.
advancements.alexsmobs.froststalker_helm: Craft a Froststalker Helmet to walk amongst Froststalkers undetected.
advancements.alexsmobs.laviathan_spyglas: Observe a Laviathan through the lens of a Spyglass.
advancements.alexsmobs.straddle_saddle.d: Craft a Straddlite Saddle. Don't forget the trim!
advancements.alexsmobs.laviathan_four_pa: Ride a Laviathan with three other passengers.
advancements.alexsmobs.cosmic_cod.title: Weird Fishes/Arpeggi
advancements.alexsmobs.cosmic_cod.desc: Create a Cosmic Cod by placing a Cod in a Capsid.
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_cosmaw.title: Its a Fish? Its a Bug? What is it?
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_cosmaw.desc: Tame a Cosmaw by feeding it Cosmic Cod.
advancements.alexsmobs.breed_anteater.de: Breed two Anteaters by feeding them pupae.
Feed a Maned Wolf an apple.
advancements.alexsmobs.rocky_roller.desc: Encounter a Rocky Roller in the dripstone caves.
advancements.alexsmobs.rocky_shell.title: Rocks Off!
advancements.alexsmobs.rocky_shell.desc: Obtain a Rocky Shell from slaying a Rocky Roller.
Craft a Rock Shell Chestplate to roll into a ball.
advancements.alexsmobs.tame_flutter.desc: Tame a Flutter by giving it multiple kinds of flowers.
advancements.alexsmobs.rainbow_jelly.des: Obtain Rainbow Jelly from a Comb Jelly. Use a sponge if you don't like what happens...
advancements.alexsmobs.rainbow_glass.des: Craft Rainbow Glass from Rainbow Jelly and Glass.
advancements.alexsmobs.bison_spyglass.de: Observe a Bison through the lens of a Spyglass.
advancements.alexsmobs.lost_tentacle.des: Obtain a Lost Tentacle from a battle between two titans.
advancements.alexsmobs.squid_grapple.des: Craft a Grappling Squok from Lost Tentacles, a crossbow and copper ingots.
